.DT
query_pages
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_pages

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_pages -  This method returns the array of useful pages in a book.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string * query_pages(object book)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^book%^RESET%^ - the book to get the pages from
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the array of pages

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/book_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the array of useful pages in a book.  It removes
torn out pages and pages which are added by specific things in the
game, like the print shop adding a fly leaf.  It just returns the text
for the pages, since this is what we are interested in.
.EP

